---
title: American-Style Beef Cottage Pie with Double Cheese & Burger Sauce
description: There are just some flavour combinations that are an undeniable hit. And, for us, it’s the mixture of tender beef mince, special
burger sauce, double cheese, sesame seeds and American-style spices that remind us of a juicy burger from our favourite
takeaway. Now, infuse those flavours into a cottage pie and you’ve got magic!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-cheeseburger-style-cottage-pie-7aa34ed1.jpg
